  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/385400/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765219286\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/385400/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765219286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/385400/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765219286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/385400/extras/34c2f3f0ca1792b32f4b1b40b5c1a90e.poster.avif?t=1765219286\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/385400/extras/34c2f3f0ca1792b32f4b1b40b5c1a90e.webm?t=1765219286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/385400/extras/34c2f3f0ca1792b32f4b1b40b5c1a90e.mp4?t=1765219286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are a weapon genius. You know everything about the gun mechanisms, ballistics, shooting skills and other.  You must create ever better and improved guns and earn money through accurate shooting. <br>  <br> Select and buy the necessary details in order to combine the weapon properties and achieve the maximal performance of fire efficiency. <br> Create a gun of your dream!",
